Ahh ok yeah I remember you saying it was at your sisters for that 
file. Usually I record in my bedroom office unless I am doing other 
methods. 

I think most of us go thru periods of adjustment or different 
perception. Perhaps over time we get better, they get clearer, and 
equipment changes to suit our needs.

You are off to a good start, you can hear them, and you record with 
the right intent. That in iteself should attract a few more to speak 
with you.

Misty


